metadata.name: LetSmile #1
metadata.description: LetSmile, it was born with the intent to thank the OG community for the support given in these months of work. Since June 22 is the birthday of our beloved artist, a special gift will be minted in the Ethereum blockchain. So far the Puppets have stood still to observe, but now the time has come to vectorize by creating new content ready to spread out style on the web3 space.
